==Nomenclature== * The [[Sea of Galilee]] is a small freshwater lake with a natural outlet, which is called Lake Tiberias or Lake Kinneret on modern Israeli maps, but its original name remains in use. * The Sea of CortÃ©s is more commonly known as the [[Gulf of California]]. * The [[Dead Sea]] is actually a lake, as is the [[Caspian Sea]] and the mainly dried up [[Aral Sea]].
